    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nS = \\int_{-2}^{2} |-x^2 + 4| dx = \\int_{-2}^{2} (-x^2 + 4) dx = \\frac{32}{3} \\text{ m}^2.\n$$"
