      647,
      1534
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Theo Viết ta có $\\begin{cases} x_1 + x_2 = k \\\\ x_1x_2 = -3 \\end{cases}$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      251,
      1548,
      370,
      1585
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "c) Đúng."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      251,
      1590,
      1409,
      1637
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Diện tích trồng Hoa Hồng là diện tích hình phẳng giới hạn bởi $(P)$ và đường thẳng $d$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      251,
      1654,
      1348,
      2212
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{align*}\n\\text{Ta có } S_{HH} &= \\int_{x_1}^{x_2} |-x^2 + 4 - (kx + 1)| dx = \\int_{x_1}^{x_2} (-x^2 - kx + 3) dx = \\int_{x_1}^{x_2} (-x^2 - kx + 3) dx \\\\\n&= \\left[ -\\frac{x^3}{3} - \\frac{kx^2}{2} + 3x \\right]_{x_1}^{x_2} = -\\frac{x_2^3}{3} - \\frac{kx_2^2}{2} + 3x_2 + \\frac{x_1^3}{3} + \\frac{kx_1^2}{2} - 3x_1 \\\\\n&= -\\frac{1}{3}(x_2^3 - x_1^3) - \\frac{k}{2}(x_2^2 - x_1^2) + 3(x_2 - x_1) = -\\frac{2x_2^3}{3} + 6x_2 \\\\\n&= -\\frac{1}{3}\\sqrt{k^2 + 12}(k^2 + 3) + \\frac{k}{2}\\sqrt{k^2 + 12} + 3\\sqrt{k^2 + 12} \\\\\n&= \\sqrt{k^2 + 12}\\left(-\\frac{k^3}{3} - 1 + \\frac{k^2}{2} + 3\\right) = \\sqrt{k^2 + 12}\\left(\\frac{k^2}{6} + 2\\right) = \\frac{(\\sqrt{k^2 + 12})^3}{6} \\ge \\frac{3\\sqrt{12}}{6}.\n\\end{align*}\n$$"
  }
